    public class InterfaceTabbedDisplayPanel
extends InterfaceDisplayPanel
implements java.beans.PropertyChangeListener, DisplayPanelListener
    This class extends InterfaceDisplayPanel in order to provide a tabbed window pane, similar to a typical web browser. It extends all the functionality necessary to do this.
    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Andrew Reid
